WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.260
Avvalroq, biz o‘zlashtirish bayonoti g‘oyasi haqida suhbatlashdik,

00:00:04.260 --> 00:00:07.570
masalan, har qanday turtle.Turtle ga o‘xshash.

00:00:07.570 --> 00:00:10.230
U tenglik belgisi o‘ng tomonidagi narsalarni oladi

00:00:10.230 --> 00:00:14.535
va uni chap tomonda nomlangan o‘zgaruvchiga tayinlaydi.

00:00:14.535 --> 00:00:18.210
Bunday holda, o‘ngdagi kod

00:00:18.210 --> 00:00:24.165
yangi turtle ob’ekti yaratadi va bu turtle ob’ekti Emi nomlangan o‘zgaruvchiga tayinlanadi

00:00:24.165 --> 00:00:27.665
Ammo biz turtle ob’ektlari bilan cheklanib qolishimiz shart emas,

00:00:27.665 --> 00:00:30.560
o‘zgaruvchiga boshqa narsalarni ham tayinlashimiz mumkin.

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:33.360
Masalan, ushbu bayonot

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:36.895
yoqimli rang deb nomlangan o‘zgaruvchiga sariq rang tayinlaydi.

00:00:36.895 --> 00:00:39.870
Keling, shunga o‘xshash narsadan qanday foydalanishimiz mumkinligini ko‘rib chiqamiz.

00:00:39.870 --> 00:00:44.635
Mana, bizning tanish kodimiz turtle da bo‘lgan "Sariq kvadrat chizish".

00:00:44.635 --> 00:00:49.810
Faqat bu yerda bu tayinlash bayonoti qo‘shib, uni biroz o‘zgartiramiz.

00:00:49.810 --> 00:00:54.140
Endi biz sariq rangni ushbu yoqimli rang o‘zgaruvchisiga qo‘ydik,

00:00:54.140 --> 00:00:58.365
biz ushbu o‘zgaruvchidan ushbu satrga muhtoj bo‘lgan kodning istalgan joyidan foydalanishimiz mumkin.

00:00:58.365 --> 00:01:01.830
Shunday qilib, ushbu chiziqqa sariq rangni qo‘yish o‘rniga,

00:01:01.830 --> 00:01:04.490
uning o‘rniga biz chiroyli rang qo‘yamiz.

00:01:04.490 --> 00:01:07.180
Bu aniq ta’sir qiladi.

00:01:07.180 --> 00:01:10.010
turtle sariq kvadratni tortadi.

00:01:10.010 --> 00:01:12.740
Yaxshi narsalardan biri, shunday qilish

00:01:12.740 --> 00:01:15.230
bu o‘zgaruvchini bir nechta joyda ishlatishimiz mumkin.

00:01:15.230 --> 00:01:19.150
Xuddi bizda boshqa turtle lar boshqa shakllarni chizishsa.

00:01:19.150 --> 00:01:21.350
biz bir xil yoqimli rang o‘zgaruvchidan foydalanib

00:01:21.350 --> 00:01:25.540
ular chizayotgan rangni ham sozlash mumkin.

00:01:26.540 --> 00:01:31.340
Agar biz sariq rang bu yoqimli rang deb o‘ylamaslikka qaror qilsak,

00:01:31.340 --> 00:01:34.075
o‘zgaruvchiga berilgan satrni o‘zgartirishimiz mumkin.

00:01:34.075 --> 00:01:37.880
Aytaylik, hozir sariq satr o‘rniga,

00:01:37.880 --> 00:01:40.655
biz ko‘k satrni tayinlaymiz.

00:01:40.655 --> 00:01:45.885
Shunday qilib, endi bu nom yoqimli rang o‘rniga deb ko‘k rangni anglatadi.

00:01:45.885 --> 00:01:51.210
Yaxshi tomoni shundaki, biz ushbu o‘zgaruvchini faqat bitta joyda o‘zgartirishimiz kerak,

00:01:51.210 --> 00:01:54.970
ammo bu satr barcha joylarda ishlatila boshlaydi.

00:01:54.970 --> 00:01:59.190
Shunday qilib, bu turtle larning barchasi hozir ochiq ko‘k rangda chizilgan.

